\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"137309c10a81927ef6c95410d842a9679f6c3fa3","tid":1738708,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b29c6b1455749159c378f4d1ce256a11b6411a9b","tid":1738708,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:24:56.000Z","msg":"要入油未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"仲燒緊柴油 <br />\nD黑煙遠到夏威夷都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecded0f43108e1c0bb5972f32bb6568c14e6fbc","tid":1738708,"uid":138713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:43:32.000Z","msg":"返歸入油啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8ceb02334b323f7b17e8402e358c2a9b007fd4","tid":1738708,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"無威脅性何來恐嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n殺平民就叻"}]}